{"tid":2154283,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"對抗健康碼輿論上講會引致第4波比講dna送中有用","createTime":"2020-08-13T04:56:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-14T01:52:11.000Z","uid":321407,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"bc549a77be9e2fd58ccbacf5bffb6b0b1f6a772e","tid":2154283,"uid":321407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T04:56:30.000Z","msg":"同啲藍屍/政府講DNA送中，佢哋只會答你防疫大撚晒，但係你同佢講會搞到爆第四波，藍屍都可能反埋一份<br />\n<br />\n簡單解釋：<br />\n<br />\n當阿A無病，去檢測，交咗樣本後先染病，咁阿A就會帶住無病碼，去嗰啲因為有咗健康碼而放寬咗嘅地方播毒---》跟住就第四波<br />\n<br />\n（扮唔係完全反健康碼）：<br />\n<br />\n健康碼要有兩個條件先有用<br />\n1. 要全港<strong>同一時間</strong>檢測+派碼<br />\n2. 檢測同派碼中間段時間要<strong>全港禁足</strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong>BUT</strong> 如果做到上面兩點，只需要將中招嘅隔離就可以，即係健康碼都係廢嘅"},{"pid":"b315a444bf564fb725b9b0b399bb6804db57503c","tid":2154283,"uid":55854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T05:07:31.000Z","msg":"幫你推"},{"pid":"c8e65454cb20f7a6846dcadeb0240b48e7f15ef1","tid":2154283,"uid":20867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T05:09:40.000Z","msg":"10:10 開始睇<br />\n(簡單易明）<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-small\">[懶人包]健康碼｜踢爆健康碼真相｜如何剝奪個人自由｜社會信用系統2.0｜完全拆解港共政權政府整盤棋局！<br />\n56,617 views</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://m.youtube.com/watch?v=tHeE6zjhFl4&amp;t=610s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DtHeE6zjhFl4%26t%3D610s&d=5A66RL0pJQ3e97MQjAwjzoc%2FDYnbIFO1z8NzTSvCTwQ%3D&h=dd0de043\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.youtube.com/watch?v=tHeE6zjhFl4&amp;t=610s</a>"},{"pid":"e63a0ab88891c101fba2e382881ebf52c7e6169c","tid":2154283,"uid":71092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T05:20:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64daa8b16b3326aca76a9d614309cc37f7d1259f","tid":2154283,"uid":71092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T05:20:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"720f3